Code Explanation
moveForward(): Both motors are set to move forward.
turnRight(): Stops the right motor and runs only the left motor to turn right.
turnLeft(): Stops the left motor and runs only the right motor to turn left.
stopMoving(): Stops both motors if the robot goes off the line entirely.

Required Components
Arduino Uno
2 IR sensors (one for left and one for right)
Motor driver module (L298N)
2 DC motors (for the left and right wheels)
Power supply (battery pack)
Jumper wires
